  "title": "SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p>Drive all the operational activities while maximizing our productivity and efficiencies, oversee P&amp;L, with an overall accountability for sales, profits, people.</p>\n<p>Manages and works closely with operation Manager to develop operational strategies to improve sales and profits.</p>\n<p>Manage and guide the operaion manager and operations team to ensure motivation, commitment, productivity, drive and pride.</p>\n<p>Responsible for achieving internal sales and profit objectives on monthly, quarterly and yearly.</p>\n<p>Analyse past financials and business information to spot trends and threats and the growth plans for the outlet.</p>\n<p>Prepare monthly budgets for costs of food, staff, operations based on past data.</p>\n<p>Responsible for all service staff and improve service standards and workflow procedures.</p>\n<p>Provide emotional and technical support to outlet management staff in order to build up motivation.</p>\n<p>Provide feedback to Operations department on day-to-day operations</p>\n<p>Develop systems which are deemed to be most appropriate for efficiency and the speed of service, which will ensure maximum customer satisfaction.</p>",
